1	// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
2	// Runner env read + validate — claude-sdk variant.
3	//
4	// Mirrors @ax/agent-native-runner's env.ts in shape, adding AX_LLM_PROXY_URL
5	// on top of the four vars the native runner needs. The claude-sdk runner
6	// additionally needs that URL so it can point `ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL` at our
7	// sandbox-internal proxy (Week 6.5d Tasks 2–4) — without it, the vendored
8	// claude-agent-sdk would try to reach api.anthropic.com directly, defeating
9	// the whole host-mediated LLM-call story.
10	//
11	// AX_RUNNER_ENDPOINT is an opaque URI (I1). The IPC client parses the
12	// scheme; see @ax/agent-runner-core/ipc-client.ts.
13	//
14	// Empty-string values are treated as missing: an env var set to '' is
15	// almost always a wiring bug, not an intentional value. Failing loud here
16	// beats a confusing downstream error.
